quran[11{c,v,t}:
39,11,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) inn se kaho, mujhe hukum diya gaya hai ke deen ko Allah ke liye khalis kar ke uss ki bandagi karoon"
39,12,aur mujhe hukum diya gaya hai ke sab se pehlay mein khud muslim banon
39,13,"kaho, agar mein apne rab ki nafarmani karoon to mujhe aik barray din ke azaab ka khauf hai"
39,14,keh do ke mein to apne deen ko Allah ke liye khalis kar ke usi ki bandagi karoon ga
39,15,"tum uss ke siwa jis jis ki bandagi karna chaho karte raho kaho, asal diwalyay to wohi hain jinhon ne qayamat ke roz apne aap ko aur apne ahal o Ayal ko ghatay mein daal diya khoob sun rakho, yahi khula dewala hai"
39,16,"unn par aag ki chutriyan oopar se bhi chhai hon gi aur neechay se bhi yeh woh injaam hai jis se Allah apne bundon ko darata hai, pas ae mere Bandoo , mere ghazab se bachcho"
39,17,bakhilaf is ke jin logon ne Taghoot ki bandagi se ijtinab kya aur Allah ki taraf rujoo kar liya unn ke liye khushkhabri hai pas ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) basharat day do mere unn bundon ko
39,18,jo baat ko ghhor se suntay hain aur is ke behtareen pehlu ki pairwi karte hain yeh woh log hain jin ko Allah ne hadaayat bakhsh hai aur yahi danishmand hain
39,19,( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) uss shakhs ko kon bacha sakta hai jis par azaab ka faisla chaspan ho chuka ho? kya tum ussay bacha satke ho jo aag mein gir chuka ho ?
39,20,"Albata jo log apne rab se dar kar rahay unn ke liye buland emiratein hain manzil par manzil bani hui, jin ke neechay nhrin beh rahi hon gi yeh Allah ka wada hai, Allah kabhi apne waday ki khilaaf warzi nahi karta"
39,21,"kya tum nahi dekhte ke Allah ne aasman se pani barsaya, phir is ko soton aur chashmo aur daryaaon ki shakal mein zameen ke andar jari kya, phir is pani ke zareya se woh terhan terhan ki khityan nkalta hai jin ki kasmain mukhtalif hain, phir woh khityan pick kar sookh jati hain, phir tum dekhte ho ke woh zard par gayeen, phir aakhir kaar Allah unn ko bhus bana deta hai Dur haqeeqat iss mein aik sabaq hai aqal rakhnay walon ke liye"
